*Drug* je preuzeo ulogu lidera u timu. (The other one took on the role of a leader in the team.)

Komšija je večeras bio u mojoj kući sa svojim *drugom*. (The neighbour was at my house tonight with his friend.)

*Drug* je prethodno radio u velikoj kompaniji. (The other one used to work in a big company.)

Naš tim je dobio *drugu* priliku da pobedi. (Our team got a second chance to win.)

Ona je našla *drugu* stranu priče. (She found the other side of the story.)